// tests/good/parameterized.bloc
block parameterized /// this is a test block definition using parameters
param NCHAN u32 default=2 min=1 max=4
param MASK  u32 default=0xF min=0 max=0xF
param HAS_ENABLE bool default=0

pin raw input ch{c:1}_in[c=NCHAN] if ((MASK>>c)&1)  /// array of input pins, optionally exported
pin raw output out /// an output pin
#if HAS_ENABLE
pin bool input enable /// optional pin
#endif

function update /// the update function
